v2.0 (2026-07-19):

 * Added Scoping class (deprecated parent variable in TeXSettings)

v1.9.20260601 (2026-06-01)

 * dictionary files now bundled into jar files

v1.9.20260528 (2026-05-28)

 * Renamed TeX Parser Library -> TeX Java Parser Library
   (package path names unchanged)

   The jar file is now texjavaparserlib.jar instead of
   texparserlib.jar

v1.9 (2026-04-25)

 * Bundled with TeX Java Help v1.3

v1.8 (2025-11-23)

 * Bundled with TeX Java Help v1.1

